Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.23,0:28:52.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我没问你让不让\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not asking permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.66,0:28:59.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-纳什队长  -什么\N{\rYUANWEN}Captain Nash. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.37,0:29:03.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-纳什队长  -嗯\N{\rYUANWEN}Captain Nash...- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.20,0:29:04.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果不是你妻子\N{\rYUANWEN}...if it wasn't for your wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.54,0:29:06.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不可能从那里逃出来\N{\rYUANWEN}I never would have made it out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.00,0:29:07.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她在哪儿\N{\rYUANWEN}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.17,0:29:09.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去救我们了\N{\rYUANWEN}Saving the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.17,0:29:11.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她当然会去\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.80,0:29:22.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘿 亨\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey, Hen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.02,0:29:26.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很抱歉打扰你工作了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm so sorry to bother you at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.02,0:29:28.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 没问题 你现在不是该去值班了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}No, it's no problem. Shouldn't you be on your shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.35,0:29:31.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还没跟奇米说过话吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You haven't spoken to Chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.69,0:29:33.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,说什么\N{\rYUANWEN}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.23,0:29:35.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 他都告诉我了 真糟糕\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay, he told me everything, and it sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.94,0:29:37.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.40,0:29:39.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我来不是为了这个\N{\rYUANWEN}But that's not why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.99,0:29:41.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这边走\N{\rYUANWEN}Through here. - Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.83,0:29:45.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是希望你能帮我个忙\N{\rYUANWEN}I was hoping you could do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.95,0:29:47.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行啊 你说\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.37,0:29:49.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你能联系海岸警卫队吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Can you call the Coast Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.37,0:29:51.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你船没了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Did you lose a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.04,0:29:53.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,还真是\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.09,0:29:56.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,鲍比和雅典娜的那艘游轮 乌诺号 我找不到它了\N{\rYUANWEN}Bobby and Athena's cruise ship, the Uno, I can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.84,0:29:58.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你来看\N{\rYUANWEN}Here, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.72,0:30:02.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是太平洋上的所有船只\N{\rYUANWEN}That is every boat on the Pacific right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.76,0:30:05.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们的船不在上面\N{\rYUANWEN}And theirs isn't on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.35,0:30:08.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也给鲍比和雅典娜打了很多次电话了\N{\rYUANWEN}I- I've tried to call Bobby and Athena numerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.06,0:30:10.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,都直接进了语音信箱\N{\rYUANWEN}It's just going straight to voicemail.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.27,0:30:11.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 但他们在海上 我觉得\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay, but they're at sea, and I think
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.31,0:30:13.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,应该是发生了热带风暴\N{\rYUANWEN}there's a tropical storm down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.36,0:30:14.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是飓风 它升级了\N{\rYUANWEN}Hurricane. It's been upgraded.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.73,0:30:16.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我得找到他们\N{\rYUANWEN}I need to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.69,0:30:19.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好 行 我去打个电话问问\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah, okay, I- I will make a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.49,0:30:20.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.87,0:31:07.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我听说你试图一个人拯救这艘船\N{\rYUANWEN}Heard you were trying to save the ship by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.37,0:31:09.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想要我们可以一起参与的活动\N{\rYUANWEN}You wanted an activity we could do together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.54,0:31:11.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在这不就有了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}I guess this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.66,0:31:13.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了 准备好了吗 开始\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right, ready? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.50,0:31:19.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,等等 手动控制在上面\N{\rYUANWEN}Wait. Manual override is up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.39,0:31:27.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了 看看我们能做点什么\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right, now. Let's see what we can do
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.76,0:31:30.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,防止这艘船\N{\rYUANWEN}about keeping this tube of doom
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.39,0:31:31.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,彻底翻掉\N{\rYUANWEN}from completely rolling on its side.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.78,0:31:43.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,鲍比 门\N{\rYUANWEN}Bobby, the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.01,0:32:05.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\rYUANWEN}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.85,0:32:18.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们上次聊的时候 你表示过一此\N{\rYUANWEN}So, the last time we spoke, you had expressed some trepidation
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.86,0:32:21.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对于你们这次游轮蜜月之旅的惶恐 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}about this honeymoon cruise you're about to go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.11,0:32:23.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,迟来的蜜月\N{\rYUANWEN}Belated honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.28,0:32:25.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而且我感觉惶恐这个词不太合适\N{\rYUANWEN}And I'm not sure"trepidation" is the right word.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.41,0:32:29.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得如果我们一结婚\N{\rYUANWEN}I just think if our honeymoon had come
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.83,0:32:32.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就去度蜜月 而不是四年之后再去\N{\rYUANWEN}at the start of our marriage rather than four years into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.08,0:32:33.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,感觉就不会这么\N{\rYUANWEN}it wouldn't feel so.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.96,0:32:35.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,严重\N{\rYUANWEN}consequential.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.83,0:32:37.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,此话怎讲\N{\rYUANWEN}How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.79,0:32:40.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我向雅典娜求婚的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, when I asked Athena to marry me,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.17,0:32:42.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她处于一种非常脆弱的状态\N{\rYUANWEN}she was in a very vulnerable place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.09,0:32:43.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们都是\N{\rYUANWEN}We both were.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.71,0:32:46.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当时我刚在失去了一个重要的人之后\N{\rYUANWEN}I- I had recently moved here from Minnesota
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.05,0:32:47.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从明尼苏达搬到这里\N{\rYUANWEN}after a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.97,0:32:50.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而她又刚结束了一段20年的婚姻\N{\rYUANWEN}And her marriage of 20 years had just imploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.93,0:32:53.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我求婚的时候我们才约会了几个月而已\N{\rYUANWEN}We were only seeing each other a few months when I proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.72,0:32:56.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有时候 从事你们这些职业的人\N{\rYUANWEN}Sometimes when people do the kinds of jobs you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.77,0:32:59.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,更能理解珍惜当下 不要过多等待的意义\N{\rYUANWEN}they understand the urgency of now, of not waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.57,0:33:04.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我求婚的时候基本就是这么说的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's pretty much what I said when I proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.82,0:33:07.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也没给她拒绝的机会\N{\rYUANWEN}Didn't really give her a chance to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.57,0:33:09.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你怕这次游轮之旅\N{\rYUANWEN}And you're afraid going on this cruise
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.37,0:33:11.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可能会给她这个机会\N{\rYUANWEN}might give her that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.16,0:33:13.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可能惶恐确实是对的形容\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe"trepidation"is the right word.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.33,0:33:15.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想听听我的建议吗\N{\rYUANWEN}My advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.12,0:33:16.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.79,0:33:18.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,享受一些和你太太独处的时光\N{\rYUANWEN}Enjoy some time alone with your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.72,0:33:34.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.36,0:33:46.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.61,0:33:50.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你没事吧  -没事\N{\rYUANWEN}Are you okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.32,0:33:51.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-没事  -没事吧\N{\rYUANWEN}- Yeah. - You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.37,0:33:52.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行 这没用\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right, that's not gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.66,0:33:55.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好 行\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI right. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.16,0:33:59.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们在里面\N{\rYUANWEN}We're in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.88,0:34:05.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们在里面\N{\rYUANWEN}We're in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.59,0:34:09.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们在里面\N{\rYUANWEN}We're in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.43,0:34:12.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,鲍比\N{\rYUANWEN}Bobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.39,0:34:15.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,鲍比\N{\rYUANWEN}Bobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.01,0:34:16.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没人能听见的\N{\rYUANWEN}Nobody's gonna hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.89,0:34:18.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这不一定的\N{\rYUANWEN}We don't know that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.39,0:34:20.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\rYUANWEN}Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.06,0:34:22.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所有人都在上救生艇\N{\rYUANWEN}Everybody's getting into the lifeboats.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.40,0:34:24.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们做了\N{\rYUANWEN}We did
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.19,0:34:26.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,必须要做的事\N{\rYUANWEN}what we had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.44,0:34:29.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,雅典娜\N{\rYUANWEN}Athena.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.82,0:34:33.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉\N{\rYUANWEN}I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.28,0:34:35.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你没必要道歉\N{\rYUANWEN}You have nothing to be sorry for.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.95,0:34:38.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 我有 如果不是我 你都不会在这里\N{\rYUANWEN}No, I do. You wouldn't even be here if it weren't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.91,0:34:40.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你都不想来着狗屁游轮旅行 是我逼你的\N{\rYUANWEN}You didn't want to come on this damn cruise. I made you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.87,0:34:42.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我他妈到底在想什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What the hell was I thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.92,0:34:45.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我怎么配得上这样第二次机会  -不不不 鲍比\N{\rYUANWEN}to deserve a second chance like this? - No, no, no, Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.13,0:34:46.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-别说了 别说了  -不\N{\rYUANWEN}Stop. Stop. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.71,0:34:48.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我配不上你 雅典娜 我从来都配不上你\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't deserve you, Athena. I never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.09,0:34:50.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你答应了我\N{\rYUANWEN}But you said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.13,0:34:52.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-再来一次我也还是会答应你的  -我无权向你求婚\N{\rYUANWEN}- And I would again. - I didn't have a right to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.09,0:34:54.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在我所做的一切之后 我没能救下我的第一个家庭\N{\rYUANWEN}Not after what I did. I couldn't save my first family.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.05,0:34:55.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也救不了你\N{\rYUANWEN}I can't save you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.81,0:34:58.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你已经救了我了\N{\rYUANWEN}You already did that, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.02,0:35:01.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,获得第二次机会的不是只有你\N{\rYUANWEN}You're not the only one getting a second chance here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.10,0:35:03.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你也没有逼我做任何事\N{\rYUANWEN}And you didn't make me do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.56,0:35:06.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在这里是因为我想\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm here because I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.15,0:35:08.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-和你一起  -雅典娜\N{\rYUANWEN}With you. - Athena...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.11,0:35:10.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的 我是很害怕\N{\rYUANWEN}And, yes, I was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.53,0:35:13.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是害怕 自己不知道要如何\N{\rYUANWEN}I was afraid that I, I wouldn't know how to be
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.07,0:35:15.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和你在一起\N{\rYUANWEN}with you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.07,0:35:17.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果没有了那些杂音的话\N{\rYUANWEN}without all the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.08,0:35:19.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我怕在我们真正独处的时候\N{\rYUANWEN}And when we were really, truly alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.58,0:35:21.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会不知道该说什么\N{\rYUANWEN}I- I- I would have nothing to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.29,0:35:24.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但现在我发现我有很多\N{\rYUANWEN}but now I find that I have lots,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.33,0:35:26.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有很多想说的\N{\rYUANWEN}lots to say
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.25,0:35:28.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但是没有时间了\N{\rYUANWEN}but not enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.05,0:35:32.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我爱你 老公\N{\rYUANWEN}I love you, husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.80,0:35:34.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我爱你 我爱你 老婆\N{\rYUANWEN}I love you. I love you, my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.93,0:35:36.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rYUANWEN}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.81,0:35:42.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,雅典娜 你抓住\N{\rYUANWEN}Athena, grab hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.81,0:35:44.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,抓住那根管子\N{\rYUANWEN}Grab hold of that pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.19,0:35:47.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.36,0:35:49.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你抓住 抓住\N{\rYUANWEN}You hold on, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.98,0:35:51.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.57,0:35:52.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.86,0:35:54.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,鲍比 鲍比\N{\rYUANWEN}Bobby! Bobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.02,0:36:24.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你坚持住 你坚持住\N{\rYUANWEN}You hang on, you hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.98,0:36:26.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,坚持住 坚持住\N{\rYUANWEN}Hang on, hang on.
